Using 
\begin_inset Formula $\mbox{area}(\triangle)=\frac{1}{2}ab\sin((a,b))$
\end_inset

, we get that the area of the triangle is 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\frac{1}{2}r(r+\Delta r)\sin\left(d\theta\right) & \approx\frac{1}{2}r(r+\Delta r)d\theta\approx\frac{1}{2}r^{2}d\theta
